	AnalogWayMidra4KAWJProtocol.ForMonitorLabel.Refresh()
end

if self.TBARdisplay == nil then return end

if self.TBARdisplay == 0 then
	self.TBARstatus = "DOWN"
	elseif self.TBARdisplay == 65535 then
	self.TBARstatus = "UP"
end

self.TBARSdisplay = pixcCommon.execAttribute(0, self.TBARSdisplay, self.TBARstatus, doSet)
return self.TBARSdisplay
